15:11:25.000Z","msg":"幾時有d大事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea06eb223aef121eab0c0c1e84f67719f7670eb9","tid":483761,"uid":3765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171129/57518917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171129%2F57518917&d=ER1fNaPKqYanJ41WBwuhi7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8d07d2e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171129%2F57518917&h=a7adad68\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171129/57518917</a><br />\n<br />\n十年44.6萬人單程證來港 中年男女升逾3倍 年輕女性佔三分一<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超書面答覆立法會議員提問時，透露過去10年，總共有445,963人持單程證來港，平均每日約122人，當中以25至34歲的女性最多，達112,205人，而15至24歲的女性就有29,555人，兩者合共佔總數32%，即接近三分之一；35至44歲的女性就有76,277人；中年男女方面，45至54歲的人士10來上升約3.5倍，由2007年的1,991人升至2017年的8,889人，而55至64歲的人士10來亦上升3倍，由2007年的790人升至2017年的3,166人。"},{"pid":"40f2efe50fa8c099a40d4133e146fc20d8bce9aa","tid":483761,"uid":39551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"香港玩完了"},{"pid":"148346ca286fdcf0af98fff06772e06cb032ac09","tid":483761,"uid":131441,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b97c9dae02b2d3df0a9c7db4a78b8c6030a69601","tid":483761,"uid":33058,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真 一大部分咪多得啲on9上大陸娶老婆囉<br />\n宜加仲要愈嚟愈多post吹奏大陸女人<br />\n同埋啲中年老坑 上大陸娶雞做老婆<br />\n條大陸妹拎到身份證之後就同你離婚 申請埋佢喺大陸嘅老襯落嚟<br />\n好心你哋叫雞還叫雞 比番啲理智</blockquote><br />\n呢個位真係要推撚到仆街<br />\n班廢老跟本係禍首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5923ee9fa78377b8